3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of CycleGANs and climate model predictions involves the application of AI techniques. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper involves training a model (CycleGAN) to learn a mapping between images, which is a machine learning task. 
5. cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper may involve natural language processing techniques to analyze climate model predictions and communicate them to the viewer.
